# VibeCoding + Web Excellence (repositorio unificado)

## VibeCoding (produto)
1. `/using-superpowers` antes de acoes com skills.
2. Fases e gates: `docs/DOCS_INDEX.md`, `WORKFLOW.md`, `docs/S03_SKILLS_INDEX.md`.
3. Skills Cursor (87 pastas): `.cursor/skills/*/SKILL.md` — invocacao `/nome` ou `@.cursor/skills/...`
4. **Skills obrigatórias por comando:** antes de seguir qualquer `.cursor/commands/**/*.md`, ler o frontmatter `skills:` e carregar cada skill listada (Read em `.cursor/skills/<nome>/SKILL.md`). Hooks (`beforeSubmitPrompt`) e `npm run verify:commands` reforçam a regra.

## Web Excellence (paginas / UI / SEO)
1. Skills com grafo (71): `.cursor/skills-web-excellence/**/*.md` — ver `SKILLS_INDEX.md` nessa pasta.
2. Agents pipeline: `.cursor/agents/AGENTS_INDEX.md` (01-architect … 07-deploy-manager + agents VibeCoding).
3. Commands: `.cursor/commands/COMMANDS_INDEX.md` (`project/`, `build/`, `generate/`, `audit/` + comandos raiz PRO).
4. Docs de referencia: `docs/web-excellence/DOCS_INDEX.md` (complementam, nao substituem PRD/spec).

## Hierarquia de rules (ordem de leitura)
1. `.cursor/rules/core/00-constitution.mdc`
2. `.cursor/rules/core/01-typescript.mdc`, `02-code-style.mdc`, `project.mdc`, `vibecoding-phases.mdc`
3. `.cursor/rules/stack/*`, `.cursor/rules/quality/*`, `.cursor/rules/design/*`
4. `.cursor/rules/domain/*`, `.cursor/rules/security/*`, `.cursor/rules/framework/*`
5. Indice completo: `.cursor/rules/RULES_INDEX.md`

## Principios Web (resumo)
- Semantic HTML, mobile-first, budgets de performance, SEO e a11y (WCAG 2.2 AA).
- Server Components por defeito; TypeScript strict; Zod em entradas externas.
- Stack real = o que esta em `package.json` + `06_SPECIFICATION`; Framer Motion e opcional (ver `stack/framer-motion.mdc`).

## Verificacao
- `bash scripts/verify-docs.sh` — gates VibeCoding
- `bash scripts/verify-docs-integrity.sh` — frontmatter/links scoped (web-excellence)
- `npm run verify:framework` — grafo skills Web Excellence
